                                            <p>Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, Company grants User a non-transferable, non-assignable, limited, non-exclusive, revokable license to use Edgar only as permitted in this Agreement, for the term of User’s Paid Subscription. The password and login information that is assigned to User must be kept confidential, may only be used by User personally, and may not be shared, given, rented, or assigned to any other persons.</p>
