                                            <p>Company reserves the right to terminate this Agreement and User’s rights hereunder, and to retain all sums paid by User, at Company’s sole discretion. The provisions of the Disclaimer and Limitation of Liability shall survive any termination of this Agreement.</p>
                                            <p>
